OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely dry and cloudy at first
OL,6,Fthis morning, with just a few showers.
OL,7,FHeavy and more persistent rain will
OL,8,Farrive this afternoon with
OL,9,Fstrengthening winds around the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRain will continue through
OL,12,Fthe evening and first part of the
OL,13,Fnight with heavy downpours at times.
OL,14,FGradually turning drier as rain clears
OL,15,Fto the east after midnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA drier start for many on
OL,18,FTuesday with some bright spells.
OL,19,FHowever, heavy scattered showers will
OL,20,Fquickly move in during the morning,
OL,21,Fwith a chance of thunder at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
