OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,6,Fspell of rain moves through on
OL,7,FWednesday, followed by heavy blustery
OL,8,Fshowers on Thursday. Drier on Friday
OL,9,Fwith some bright spells and a few
OL,10,Fshowers at times.
